OL,3,CBlur bassist Alex James to headline
OL,4,CJersey's Weekender Festival
OL,6,FThe bassist from the Britpop band
OL,7,FBlur, Alex James, has been announced
OL,8,Fas the headliner for this year's
OL,9,FWeekender Festival in Jersey.
OL,11,FAlex James was part of one of the most
OL,12,Fsuccessful Britpop bands of the 1990s
OL,13,Fand will perform in People's Park on
OL,14,F11 September.
OL,16,FHe says: "We're taking the biggest
OL,17,Fanthems of a generation- Blur, Oasis,
OL,18,FPulp, Supergrass, The Verve and more -
OL,19,Fand we're blowing them up with a full
OL,20,F38-piece orchestra and special guest
OL,21,Fvocalists.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
