PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780337465
OL,3,CBlur bassist Alex James to headline
OL,4,CJersey's Weekender Festival
OL,6,F"It's loud, it's cinematic, and it's
OL,7,Fgoing to be legendary. See you down
OL,8,Fthe front."
OL,10,FThe event will span two days, starting
OL,11,Fon 11 September at 5pm until 1am, and
OL,12,Fon Saturday 12 September from 3pm to
OL,13,F11pm.
OL,15,FFormerly known as Jersey Live, the
OL,16,Ffestival saw dance music band
OL,17,FFaithless, including Sister Bliss and
OL,18,FRollo, followed by British pop girl
OL,19,Fgroup Sugababes, Mutya Buena, Keisha
OL,20,FBuchanan and Siobhan Donaghy, headline
OL,21,Fin 2025.
OL,26,@|D@Srp
