OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1780337465
OL,3,CBlur bassist Alex James to headline
OL,4,CJersey's Weekender Festival
OL,6,FCommenting on this year's opening
OL,7,Fheadliner, festival organiser, Warren
OL,8,FLe Sueur, says: "Bringing Britpop to
OL,9,FJersey is going to be electric.
OL,11,F"This isn't just a trip down memory
OL,12,Flane- it's a massive, symphonic
OL,13,Fmasterpiece you have to see to believe.
OL,15,F"Splitting Friday and Saturday into
OL,16,Fstandalone events lets us curate two
OL,17,Ftotally unique, heavy-hitting
OL,18,Fexperiences."
OL,20,FTickets will go on sale at the
OL,21,Fbeginning of June.
